  "title": "Prima Deli Service Crew",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>Now Hiring: PrimaDéli Full / Part Time Service Crew</p><p>We are looking for enthusiastic and hardworking individuals to join our team at PrimaDéli. If you are passionate about food, customer service, and want to be part of a dynamic team, we’d love to hear from you!</p><p>Position: PrimaDéli Service Crew</p><p>Location: Bukit Panjang Plaza</p><p>Industry: Food Retail (Waffles, Bread, and Deli Items)</p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li><p>Serve customers with a smile and ensure excellent service</p></li><li><p>Prepare and sell fresh waffles and bread products</p></li><li><p>Assist customers in placing orders for cakes, collection of cakes and product recommendation</p></li><li><p>Cleaning of trays, utensils, tongs, display cases, etc to uphold hygiene standards</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness, organization, attractiveness of product displays & ensure products neatly arranged and properly labelled.</p></li><li><p>Assist in daily, stock-taking inventory replenishment, and inventory management</p></li><li><p>Handle cash and process payments accurately</p></li><li><p>Clean the shop by end of the business day to prepare for the next day</p></li><li><p>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned by the Supervisor/Manager</p></li></ul><p>Qualifications:</p><ul><li><p>SG/PR/LTVP</p></li><li><p>No experience necessary, but customer service experience is a plus</p></li><li><p>Must have a positive attitude and a passion for food and customer service</p></li><li><p>Ability to commit to our schedule</p></li></ul><p>How to Apply:</p><p>Apply here or send your resume to yxydbiz@gmail.com. We look forward to meeting you!</p>",
